00051 PIZQueue *pizQueueNew (void)
00052 {
00053     PIZQueue *x = NULL;
00054         
00055     if (x = (PIZQueue *)malloc (sizeof(PIZQueue))) {
00056         x->count        = 0;
00057         x->poppedValue  = -1;
00058         x->head         = NULL;
00059         x->tail         = NULL;
00060     }
00061     
00062     return x;
00063 }

00065 void pizQueueFree (PIZQueue *x)
00066 {
00067     if (x) {
00068         pizQueueClear (x);
00069         free (x);
00070     }
00071 }

00073 void pizQueueClear (PIZQueue *x)
00074 {
00075     PIZQueueElement *theElement = x->head;
00076     
00077     while (theElement) {
00078         PIZQueueElement *elementToBeRemoved = NULL;
00079 
00080         elementToBeRemoved  = theElement;
00081         theElement          = elementToBeRemoved->next;
00082 
00083         free (elementToBeRemoved);
00084         elementToBeRemoved = NULL;
00085     }
00086         
00087     x->count        = 0;
00088     x->poppedValue  = -1;
00089     x->head         = NULL;
00090     x->tail         = NULL;
00091 }

00093 PIZError pizQueueAppend (PIZQueue *x, long value)
00094 {
00095     long            err = PIZ_MEMORY;
00096     PIZQueueElement *newElement = NULL;
00097     
00098     if (newElement = (PIZQueueElement *)malloc (sizeof(PIZQueueElement))) {
00099         err = PIZ_GOOD;
00100         
00101         if (x->count) {
00102             newElement->value    = value;
00103             newElement->previous = x->tail;
00104             newElement->next     = NULL;
00105             
00106             x->count ++;
00107             
00108             x->tail->next   = newElement;
00109             x->tail         = newElement;
00110             
00111         } else {
00112         
00113             newElement->value    = value;
00114             newElement->previous = NULL;
00115             newElement->next     = NULL;
00116             
00117             x->count ++;
00118             
00119             x->head = newElement;
00120             x->tail = newElement;
00121         }
00122     }
00123     
00124     return err;
00125 }

00127 PIZError pizQueuePop (PIZQueue *x)
00128 {
00129     long            err = PIZ_ERROR;
00130     PIZQueueElement *theElement = NULL;
00131     
00132     if (x->count == 1) {
00133         theElement      =  x->head;
00134         x->poppedValue  = theElement->value;
00135         
00136         free (theElement);
00137         theElement = NULL;
00138         
00139         x->count = 0;
00140         x->head  = NULL;
00141         x->tail  = NULL;
00142         
00143         err = PIZ_GOOD;
00144         
00145     } else if (x->count > 1) {
00146     
00147         theElement                  = x->head;
00148         theElement->next->previous  = NULL;
00149         
00150         x->count --;
00151         
00152         x->poppedValue  = theElement->value;
00153         x->head         = theElement->next;
00154         
00155         free (theElement);
00156         theElement = NULL;
00157         
00158         err = PIZ_GOOD;
00159     }
00160     
00161     return err;
00162 }

00164 PIZError pizQueuePopLastValue (PIZQueue *x)
00165 {
00166     long            err = PIZ_ERROR;
00167     PIZQueueElement *theElement = NULL;
00168     
00169     if (x->count == 1) {
00170         theElement      = x->tail;
00171         x->poppedValue  = theElement->value;
00172         
00173         free (theElement);
00174         theElement = NULL;
00175         
00176         x->count = 0;
00177         x->head  = NULL;
00178         x->tail  = NULL;
00179         
00180         err = PIZ_GOOD;
00181         
00182     } else if (x->count > 1) {
00183     
00184         theElement                  = x->tail;
00185         theElement->previous->next  = NULL;
00186         
00187         x->count --;
00188         
00189         x->poppedValue  = theElement->value;
00190         x->tail         = theElement->previous;
00191         
00192         free (theElement);
00193         theElement = NULL;
00194         
00195         err = PIZ_GOOD;
00196     }
00197     
00198     return err;
